  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2004-06-25",
    "date": "2004-09-14T20:37:09Z",
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to revise the tax credit for household and dependent care services necessary for gainful employment by: (1) allowing a credit amount of $3,000 for each qualifying individual; (2) increasing to $125,000 the adjusted gross income threshold amount at which credit amounts are reduced; (3) providing for an inflation adjustment to such credit and threshold amounts; and (4) making the credit refundable."
